title: Littlest noteboo
author: misnis
pages:
#- Mining checklist

-Bucket of water
-Cobblestone 1 stack
-Picks
-8 wood or 1 stack sticks
-crafting table or 1 wood
-Torches 1 stack +
-Food!
-Sword
-Shovels
#- Caving checklist

-Picks
-Bucket
-Food
-Cobblestone, 3-4 stacks
-Torches, 1+ stack
-Shovel
-Stone axe
-Crafting table
-Wood or sticks
#- Building checklist

-All materials
-Torches
-Sand or dirt for scaffolding
-Food
-Shovel
-Tools needed for material
#- Exploration checklist

-Food
-Torches 1/2 stack or less
-Blocks of dirt or cobble
-Shovel
-Pick
-More food

(if nether)

- More blocks
- More picks
