#- Alchemy table

Water + nether wart =
Awkward potion (Awd)

Awd + gold carrot =
Night vision potion
Extended: add redstone

Night vis + fermented spider eye =
Invisibility potion
Extended: add redstone
#- Awd + magma cream =
Fire resistance potion
Extended: Add restone

Fire res + Fermented spider eye =
Potion of Slowness
Extended: Add redstone

Awd + sugar =
Swiftness potion
Extended: Add redstone
Stronger: Add glowstone
#- Awd + glistering melon =
Healing potion
Stronger: Add glowstone

Healing + Fermented spider eye =
Harming potion
Stronger: Add glowstone

Awd + spider eye =
Poison
Extended: Add redstone
Stronger: Add glowstone
#- Poison + Fermented spider eye =
Harming

Awd + Ghast tear =
Regeneration potion
Extended: Add redstone
Stronger: Add glowstone

Regen + Fermented spider eye =
Weakness potion
Extended: Add redstone
#- Awd + Fermented spider eye =
Weakness potion

Awd +  Blaze powder =
Strength potion
Extended: Add redstone
Stronger: Add glowstone

Strength + Fermented spider eye =
Weakness potion
#- Unusual alchemy ingredients:

Blaze powder: 
Blaze rods

Magma cream:
Slime + blaze powder

Fermented spider eye:
Spider eye + brown mushroom + sugar
#- Golden carrot:
Carrot surrounded by golden nuggets

Glistering melon:
Melon + golden nugget
#- 
#- Fireworks and how to make them

How to make a rocket:

S-S-S
 -P- 
g-g-g

g = gunpowder
Add 1-3 gunpowder depending on how high the rocket should fly.
#- P = single piece of paper

S = at least one firework star. Add up to three for more effects.

How to make firework stars
----------------------------
one gunpowder
one dye of your choice
optional: 1 shape item
optional: 1-2 effect items
#- Shape items
These determine the shape of the explosion.

Default (no shape item):
Small ball shape

Fire charge:
Large ball shape

Gold nugget:
Star shape
#- Feather:
Burst shape

Head (only wither heads if not in creative mode):
Creeper face shape


#- Effect items
You can add either of these or both to make your firework extra fancy.

Diamond: 
Trail effect

Glowstone dust:
Twinkle (crackling) effect
#- 





wow, fireworks sure are hella complicated.
